agneekaal is a 1990 indian bollywood film produced by ranjit herma on siddharth pictures banner and directed by abbas-mustan .   starring raj babbar , jeetendra , madhavi , sonu walia and music composed by pankaj bhatt .   it is the debut hindi movie for director duo abbas-mustan .   they have made gujarathi movies earlier .   the movie has famous song " pankhida o pankhida "